data.description: Looking for a Beautiful Updated Country Ranch? You will definitely want to come take a look at this nicely updated 3 bedroom 2 bath lovely home that is brand new to the market offering over 2,000 Sq Ft of living space.  Sitting on 6 scenic acres in Bristolville Twp.   2 car attached garage. Really Nice curb appeal!  Plenty of cabinets and counter space in stunning bright open kitchen with breakfast bar seating and rustic beams. Inviting Stone Fireplace with wood burning insert for extra comfort this winter in spacious living room. Wonderful Open dining area. New interior and exterior lighting.  All brand-new vinyl windows. First Floor laundry off the kitchen.  Updated electrical 200-amp service. Back deck and patio for our door entertaining.  Updated septic system. 24x24 heated pole barn has been insulated for multi-purpose use. 12x16 shed is great for extra storage. Close to all amenities. 1 year home warranty is also included.   You could be celebrating the new year 2024 with a new home that is move in ready!
